    "SUMMARY": "Héctor Omar Ramos Lebrón (born 4 May 1990), also known as Pito Ramos or simply Pito, is a Puerto Rican footballer, who plays as a forward for Metropolitan FA and the Puerto Rico national team. He is the older brother of Heliot Ramos, a baseball player for the San Francisco Giants, and Henry Ramos, also a professional baseball player for the Doosan Bears of the Korean Baseball Organization."
